{"id":1176,"date":"2025-04-11T00:06:04","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T17:06:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1176"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:39:25","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:39:25","slug":"vi-kim-sinh-hoc-mun-san","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/vi-kim-sinh-hoc-mun-san\/","title":{"rendered":"Vi kim sinh h\u1ecdc m\u1ee5n s\u1ea7n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n s\u1ea7n vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9, da l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ti\u1ebft gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ee3i b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ea9y l\u00f9i nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Vi kim sinh h\u1ecdc k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c m\u1ee5n ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n: Retinol, Sulfur, AHA, BHA, Bakuchiol v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ng sinh th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi,<br \/>\nt\u00e1i t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng tr\u00ean da v\u00e0 gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n vi\u00eam k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Si\u00eau vi Nano th\u1ea5m th\u1ea9u v\u00e0o da, \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec da, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kho\u1ea3ng 01 ti\u1ebfng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 &#8211; 05 bu\u1ed5i,<br \/>\nkho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 21 &#8211; 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 57px; top: 212.866px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9, da l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3541,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[33],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1176","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-peel","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1176","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1176"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3541"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1176"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1176"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1176"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=1176"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.